1175.name: Dur 64
1175.Applications: This electrode with a recovery of 190% can be used for overlays with extremely abrasive and sliding wear resistance, but with middle impact.
1175.Suitable_For: Sugar mill knives and hammers, clinker crushers, sintering lines, fire gratings, mixer blades, gravel washing equipment, ceramic mixer blades, mill rollers, stone crushers, extruders etc….
